## Sitemap  
**Home Page (index.html):**
  - Logo
  - Welcome message: "Where Heavenly Sweetness Meets Daily Bread."
  - Navigation bar to all pages.
  - Highlighted product categories (cakes, cookies, brownies, pastries, snacks).
  - Daily inspiration section with Bible verses.
  - Footer with bakery interior image.


**About (about.html)**

- Sweet Manna and its founder.
- Mission & Vision statements.
- Core Values
- Story of Sweet Manna
- Team section (bakers, decorators, customer service, delivery).
- Contact info at the bottom.
- Footer with bakery interior image.



**Products (products.html)**

- Logo
- Navigation
- Menu with prices & images:
  - Cakes 
  - Cupcakes 
  - Biscuits & Cookies 
  - Brownies & Bars 
  - Pastries
  - Sweet Snacks 
- Delivery & checkout form.
- Scripture highlight: "Give us today our daily bread." – Matthew 6:11
- Footer with bakery interior image.

**Gallery (gallery.html)**

- Logo
- Navigation
- Image showcase of all products with labels (cakes, cupcakes, cookies, pastries, brownies, and sweet snacks).
- Footer with bakery interior image.

**Contact Us (contact_us.html)**

- logo
- Nagivation
- Physical address, email & phone number.
- Contact form (name, email, message).
- Google Maps embed for bakery location.
- Footer with bakery interior image.

**Enquiry (enquiry.html)**

- Logo  
- Navigation (updated to include Enquiry page)  
- Enquiry form with fields: Name, Email, Subject, Message  
- Dynamic submission confirmation via script.js  
- Linked CSS styling consistent with other pages  
- SEO meta tags: title, description, keywords, author  
- Social media links in footer  
- Footer with bakery interior image  


